/P 48 0 R
/T (Log Rotation Reports older than 30 days are automatically pruned. The setup_cron.sh rotate command uses find with -mtime +30 -delete to clean both the reports and logs directories. An optional logrotate configuration is also written to /etc/logrotate.d/sys_audit for daily compression and 30-day retention.)
/E (Log Rotation Reports older than 30 days are automatically pruned. The setup_cron.sh rotate command uses find with -mtime +30 -delete to clean both the reports and logs directories. An optional logrotate configuration is also written to /etc/logrotate.d/sys_audit for daily compression and 30-day retention.)
/Pg 12 0 R
/K [17]
>>
endobj
190 0 obj
<<
/Type /StructElem
/S /H3
