634 0 obj
<<
/Title (This project was developed as part of the NSCS Operating Systems course for Academic Year 2025/2026. The objective is to design and implement a fully automated Linux-based system audit and monitoring solution using Bash shell scripting. The system collects detailed hardware and software information, generates structured reports in multiple formats, transmits reports via email, automates execution through cron jobs, and supports remote monitoring via SSH.)
/Dest [10 0 R /Fit]
/Parent 573 0 R
/Next 635 0 R
>>
